{"about_the_game":"Settlemoon is an old-school idle game about building a small sidescrolling town. As your town grows in real time, you'll attract visitors, buy materials, sell items, and post quests for adventurers to complete. Expand from a single inn to a bustling town that visitors of all levels and classes are attracted to.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443780/extras/store_page_preview_build.gif?t=1711374050\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Relaxed commitment</h2>Good things take time. Set up your town and check in to see who's visiting throughout the day, or set things up to run overnight. Your town will handle itself for a while, even when the game isn't open, and will be there waiting for your return.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mysterious World</h2>With no fail states and no need for constant micromanagement, you can study Settlemoon's inner workings at your own pace. Attract odd visitors and powerful bosses to uncover the mystery of the land, all told through charming pixel art and a retro-inspired soundtrack.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443780/extras/store_page_preview_quest.gif?t=1711374050\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize your town</h2>Using hundreds of different pieces of decor, paint colors and flooring, pretty up your town however you like. Re-shape your town to suit the needs of yourself and your visitors. Create quests for adventurers to go on to build your town's economy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fashion and Favorites</h2>Every adventurer has a unique look. Name your favorites so you'll see them revisit, or copy their fashion sense to your own avatar. You can also just fling them around. They can take it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443780/extras/store_page_preview_comein.gif?t=1711374050\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Founder","pa